title: The Velvet Underground Discography (Remastered)
description:
Their four original studio albums, plus the 1985 VU compilation album, all sourced from the recent reissues of their entire catalogue. 
I've removed the studio chatter on the beginning of Foggy Notion, otherwise they are the same as on the reissues.

1967 - The Velvet Underground & Nico
1968 - White Light/White Heat
1969 - The Velvet Underground
1970 - Loaded
1985 - VU (Recorded 1968/69)

Enjoy!!
